            <p>Founded in 2018, Whiskers Haven is a no-kill shelter dedicated to rescuing abandoned and stray cats from our community. We provide medical care, nutritious food, and plenty of love while we search for their perfect forever homes.</p>
            <p>Our experienced team of volunteers and veterinary partners ensure every cat receives the attention and care they deserve. We believe that no cat should be left behind, and we work tirelessly to give each one a new beginning.</p>
